milestones.description: Campbell and Andy Flower's 92-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 81 between Kevin Arnott and Ali Shah
Mahanama has scored 3 hundreds in ODIs, the most for SL breaking Roy Dias's record
Zimbabwe's 3-run win against Sri Lanka is the smallest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 9-run win against England
